Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=14}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nãaao!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.97,0:01:57.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou caindo! Estou caindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou caindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Aterrissamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cara, estou exausto.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.87,0:02:21.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't "we've landed" me! I thought I'd die! - OG}Não me venha com "aterrissamos"!\NEu achei que ia morrer!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que mais a gente podia ter feito?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.62,0:02:27.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was you who said\Nthat we couldn't use the elevator so they wouldn't find us! - OG}Você é que disse que não podíamos usar\No elevador pra eles não nos acharem!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.92,0:02:30.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even so, you didn't have to jump off! - OG}Mesmo assim, não precisava pular!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're not that shipwright with a square nose! - OG}Você não é aquele carpinteiro narigudo!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.67,0:02:35.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Eu... Desculpa.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, fine. At least it did get us down. - OG}Bom, tudo bem. Pelo menos descemos.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.10,0:02:39.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If it was okay, then don't hit me! - OG}Se está tudo bem, então não me bate!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But... this may be kinda bad. - OG}{We may be in some trouble. - JT}Mas... a situação parece bem ruim.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ruim? O que é ruim?{OG}{Trouble? What trouble? - JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This island's geography and the weather. - OG}{This island's topography and climate. - JT}A geografia e o clima dessa ilha.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com todo esse vento soprando,\Nse a pressão atmosférica cair,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.91,0:02:58.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{a typhoon might come through here tonight. - OG}um tufão pode passar por aqui essa noite.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa cidade é chamada de Cidade da Água.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.16,0:03:04.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In other words, it can be a weak point\Nthat could easily lead to flood damage. - OG}Ou seja, é propensa\Na sofrer danos de enchente.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E daí? Qual o problema?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.67,0:03:10.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... It bothers me a little,\Nso I'll check into it later. - OG}Bom, me preocupa um pouco,\Nentão vou verificar mais tarde.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, let's go back to the inn. - OG}Enfim, vamos voltar pra pousada.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.30,0:03:21.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seguindo o alerta de Aqua Laguna\Nemitido para toda a ilha,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.97,0:03:27.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{the shipbuilding factory and docks on Shipyard Island will be opened as evacuation centers. - OG}{\q2}todas as fábricas de navios e docas na\NIlha do Estaleiro serão abertas como centros de evacuação.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Large crowds are expected,\Nso please evacuate ahead of time. - OG}{\i1}Esperamos grandes multidões,\Nentão por favor evacuem o mais rápido possível.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.32,0:03:38.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{In addition, since Dock One\Nis currently in a dangerous state... - OG}Além disso, como a Doca Um\Nestá atualmente em estado perigoso...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, I'll put the iron board on. - OG}Certo, vou colocar a placa de ferro.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys have everything you need? - OG}Vocês têm tudo que precisam?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.04,0:03:47.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim. Vamos evacuar pro estaleiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.42,0:03:50.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, hold on a bit.\NI'd better fill the gap good with hempen. - OG}Bom, espera um pouco.\NÉ melhor eu vedar bem a fresta com corda.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If the inside of our house gets flooded,\Neverything will be ruined.}Se a nossa casa inundar,\Nvai estragar tudo.{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.96,0:04:00.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, o vento está ficando forte!\NPreparem-se pras ondas!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.51,0:04:04.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Guys! If we're taking our time,\Nassassin pirates will show up too this time! - OG}Pessoal! Se demorarmos,\Npiratas assassinos vão aparecer!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é assustador!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra onde ele sumiu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que ele veio por aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele ainda deve estar por perto!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.94,0:04:12.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, you guys go search over there. - OG}Certo, vocês vão procurar lá.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.78,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Que droga está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.95,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why am I being chased after? I don't get it! - OG}Por que estão me perseguindo? Não entendo!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So this is the reason\Nthey've been chasing after me! - OG}Então {\i1}esse{\i0} é o motivo!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Assassination culprits? - OG}Somos uma tripulação de assassinos?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.05,0:04:43.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This bites. I can't even go back\Nto the inn like this.}Que saco. Agora nem posso\Nvoltar pra pousada.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ah... Who is it over there?! - OG}Ah... Quem está ali?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This way! I found a suspicious guy here! - OG}{This way! A shady guy's over here! - JT}Por aqui! Encontrei alguém suspeito!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you sure, landlord? - OG}Tem certeza, dono da pousada?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.02,0:04:55.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes. Those pirates have been staying\Nat this inn since last night. - OG}Sim. Esses piratas estão hospedados\Nna minha pousada desde ontem à noite.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They were there until just a bit ago. - OG}Eles estavam aqui agora mesmo...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estavam aqui?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.95,0:04:59.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.86,0:05:05.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ainda têm muita bagagem\Nno quarto, talvez voltem.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, então! Vocês, fiquem aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The rest of you, let's go search this area together! - OG}O resto de nós vai vasculhar a área!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escutem, procurem em\Ncada canto pra encontrá-los!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, não tem ninguém aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é mesmo o navio deles?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com certeza! Olha!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's the Straw Hats' pirate flag. - OG}Essa é a bandeira dos Piratas do Chapéu de Palha.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.28,0:05:40.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aposto que já abandonaram o navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse navio está todo arrebentado.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How was it? DId you find them? - OG}E aí? Encontraram eles?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, eles não estão aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There isn't much stuff inside the ship.\NThis ship definitely is abandoned. - OG}Não tem quase nada dentro.\NEles devem ter abandonado o navio.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go look someplace else. - OG}Vamos procurar em outro lugar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.31,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem eram eles?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.39,0:06:17.15,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que algo está acontecendo na cidade?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Encontraram eles?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! Where are they?! - OG}Droga! Onde eles estão...?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? What is it, Nami? - OG}Hm? O que foi, Nami?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você acha que todo mundo está bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os carpinteiros estão por toda a cidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.04,0:06:40.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I think Chopper and Sanji-kun are okay since their faces are still unknown, but... - OG}Acho que o Chopper e o Sanji ficam bem\Njá que os rostos deles ainda são desconhecidos.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At any rate, let's hurry! - OG}Vamos nos apressar!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.39,0:06:49.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O sea train ainda está funcionando...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.35,0:06:55.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like the afternoon train has already left, but there's another one that departs at night in this bad weather? - OG}{\q2}O trem da tarde já partiu, mas parece que\Nainda tem uma partida noturna apesar do tempo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.65,0:07:01.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{11 p.m., leaving for Enies Lobby... The sea train is pretty impressive. - OG}Com destino a Enies Lobby às onze da noite...\NO sea train é bem impressionante.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Alguma informação sobre os piratas?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não. Nada.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.03,0:07:09.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we can just capture one and squeeze 'em,\Nthey'll spill the beans on the rest. - OG}Se conseguirmos capturar um e apertá-lo,\Nele vai entregar o resto.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up! Before the waves get high! - OG}Rápido, antes das ondas ficarem altas demais!{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que a Robin embarcou no sea train.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.58,0:07:20.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se ela embarcou, a coisa não podia ficar pior.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.88,0:07:24.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When Water Seven\Nis already too big to handle... - OG}Water 7 já é difícil o suficiente de lidar...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.55,0:07:28.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if... I did something\Nto upset her at the bookstore. - OG}Será que eu fiz algo\Npra irritá-la na livraria.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu bobo. Não tem como ser isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.60,0:07:31.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, hey, excuse me. - OG}Ah, ei, com licença.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês viram uma mulher bonita assim?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that... The pretty woman who's 20\Nyears older than in that picture, right? - OG}Ah... Você quer dizer a mulher bonita\Nque estava assim vinte anos atrás?{Gaijin/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.31,0:07:41.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I had, I would've told either\Nthe paper company or Galley-La immediately. - OG}Se eu tivesse visto, teria avisado\No jornal ou a Galley-La na hora.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas pensar que ela é uma assassina...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que surpresa, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.78,0:07:50.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, it's fine if you wanna look for the culprits, but you should evacuate soon. - OG}Bom, é legal vocês procurarem\Nos culpados, mas deviam evacuar logo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Or you'll be swallowed by Aqua Laguna. - OG}Ou a Aqua Laguna vai engolir vocês.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well then, see ya. - OG}Até mais.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Things are going wrong for all of us, too... - OG}As coisas estão dando errado pra todos nós.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.84,0:08:05.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que o Luffy e os outros estão bem.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.42,0:08:09.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Luffy tá bem. Quem me preocupa é a Nami{-san}.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.43,0:08:14.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At any rate, the town\Nis becoming quite empty. - OG}A cidade está ficando bem vazia.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.52,0:08:20.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O vento está ficando cada vez mais forte.\NAs pessoas já começaram a evacuar.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Robin{-chan}!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você foi?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.45,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse cheiro... Será que é...?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Chopper, what's the matter?! - OG}Chopper, o que houve?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Espera!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.13,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela está aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chopper!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Ops!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, você tá bem?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper! Você tá bem?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você se machucou?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.56,0:09:06.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez, don't be reckless!\NWhat on earth is going on... - OG}Para, não seja imprudente!\NQue diabos está acontecendo?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.48,0:09:10.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Starting to run so sudden... ly... - OG}Você saiu correndo tão de repen... te...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Robin!\N– Robin{-chan}!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.37,0:09:19.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você esteve?!\NA gente te procurou por toda parte!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Everyone's worried about you! - OG}Todo mundo está preocupado!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, let's go back to the inn together. - OG}Vamos, vamos voltar pra pousada.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, a lot has happened while you've been gone. I'll explain in detail. - OG}Muita coisa aconteceu desde que\Nvocê sumiu. Vou te explicar tudo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas essa distância é irritante.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Já vou até aí!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, tudo bem. Fiquem aí.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't...- OG}Eu não vou...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.02,0:09:43.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{return to you guys. - OG}voltar pra vocês.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.94,0:09:47.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossos caminhos se separam aqui... nesta cidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Que está dizendo, Robin{-chan}?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I get it. You're thinking about the newspaper, right? - OG}Ah, entendi. É por causa do jornal, né?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about it! - OG}Não se preocupe com isso!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{None of us believe it, - OG}Nenhum de nós acredita nisso.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.79,0:10:02.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and being falsely accused\Nof a crime often happens to pirates! - OG}Piratas são acusados falsamente o tempo todo!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.42,0:10:07.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry for pinning\Nan unreasonable crime on you guys. - OG}Me desculpem por terem sido incriminados\Npor um crime tão absurdo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.96,0:10:12.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas o artigo está dizendo a verdade.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.01,0:10:16.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It really was me who infiltrated\Nthe mayor's residence last night. - OG}Fui eu mesma que invadi\Na residência do prefeito ontem à noite.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.47,0:10:23.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I carry a darkness within me\Nthat you guys all don't know about.-OG}Nenhum de vocês conhece\Na escuridão que carrego dentro de mim.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa escuridão vai destruir vocês algum dia.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.28,0:10:34.70,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{The organizations Nico Robin had something to do with up until today all got annihilated... - OG}Até hoje, toda organização que\Nacolheu Nico Robin foi aniquilada.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.70,0:10:37.62,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{except for her. - OG}{She's the only survivor. - JT}Mas ela sobreviveu todas as vezes.{Z}{LRLL Ep.6 16:38)}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.62,0:10:44.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, estou colocando a culpa em\Nvocês e planejando fugir.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The situation will get worse. - OG}A situação só vai piorar.{JT/Z}{Used as flashback at 19:10}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que quer dizer?! Por que você está–
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.00,0:10:53.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why I'm doing it...\NIt's something you don't need to know. - OG}Por que estou fazendo isso... é algo\Nque vocês não precisam saber.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.22,0:10:59.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin{-chan}! Não entendo o que está dizendo!\NO que aconteceu com você?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin! Vamos voltar juntos!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.35,0:11:08.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Although I only spent a short time\Nwith you, after today... - OG}Passei pouco tempo\Ncom vocês, mas depois de hoje...{JT}{Used as flashback at 19:10}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nunca mais vou ver vocês.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.61,0:11:16.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thank you for being nice to a person like me. - OG}Obrigada por serem tão gentis\Ncom alguém como eu.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Goodbye. - OG}Adeus.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.05,0:11:38.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei... espera...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não consigo...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,aceitar isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.77,0:11:45.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para de brincadeira!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Robin{-chan}!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.95,0:11:56.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin{-chan}!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Robin{-chan}! Robin{-chan}!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Perdi ela de vista.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.89,0:12:26.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.06,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.06,0:12:31.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You go join Luffy and the others\Nand tell them everything that just happened... - OG}Vai encontrar o Luffy e os outros\Ne conta tudo o que acabou de acontecer.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.06,0:12:34.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{without leaving a single word out. - OG}Não deixe de fora uma palavra sequer.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're you gonna do? - OG}E você?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos separar aqui por um tempo.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.11,0:12:42.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, não se preocupe.\NEu não vou fazer nada imprudente.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra onde eles foram?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olhem em cada canto!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E os becos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Couldn't they have climbed\Nup on some rooftop?! - OG}Será que estão nos telhados?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! They shook us off?! - OG}Droga! Perdemos eles!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eles com certeza correram nessa direção!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shall we check over there?! - oG}Devíamos verificar ali?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then, we'll search inside the buildings! - OG}E nós vamos procurar dentro dos prédios!{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right, then! Let's split\Ninto two groups and search! - OG}Certo! Vamos nos dividir e ir!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já dá?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda não.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde vocês perderam eles?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais um pouco.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.55,0:13:45.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come back some other time!\NI'm evacuating now. Stop pestering me! - OG}Você vai ter que voltar quando eu não\Nestiver no meio de uma evacuação. Agora, xô!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor... Eu tenho dinheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.02,0:13:54.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As much lumber, tar,\Nand rope as this amount will buy... - OG}Tanta madeira, alcatrão\Ne corda quanto isso puder comprar...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.81,0:13:58.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E também pregos, trincos e chapas de estanho.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou fechando a loja.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.53,0:14:02.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... Desculpa, mas...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está bem, então.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But you can't buy that much\Nwith this little money. - OG}Mas esse dinheiro não é suficiente pra tudo isso.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.75,0:14:17.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Então, pra compensar o resto,\Ngostaria de trocar minhas ferramentas.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, não seja ridículo! Para com isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.71,0:14:24.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I only sell. To think you're tryin' to barter...\NWhat are you, a kind of bumpkin? - OG}Só aceito dinheiro! Querendo trocar...\NVocê é algum tipo de caipira?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... You win. - OG}Tá bom, você venceu.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.44,0:14:42.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-Hey! Are you okay carrying that stuff\Nwhen you're injured that badly? - OG}E-Ei! Você devia carregar tudo isso\Nmachucado desse jeito?{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Surely you have friends, right?! Hey! - OG}Você não tem amigos\Nque possam ajudar?! Não tem?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Viu, o que eu disse?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey... Hold on a sec, lad! - OG}Ei... Espera aí, garoto!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô bem. Isso não é nada.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.35,0:15:12.98,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is it? Are you gonna... - OG}O que é? Vai me ajud–{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Toma. Leva isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá com fome, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.45,0:15:29.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sure... Be careful going back. - OG}Claro. Cuidado na volta.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Be careful going back! - OG}Cuidado na volta!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá muito bom isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a considerate pops he was. - OG}Que cara atencioso...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The waves are getting quite high. - OG}As ondas estão ficando bem altas.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe. Vai ficar tudo bem.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.93,0:16:33.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're a ship... that flew in the sky! - OG}Você é um navio que voou pelo céu!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's the matter, all of a sudden? - OG}O que deu em você, de repente?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Franky?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bro?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou ficando irritado!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez seja hora\Nde causar mais confusão!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bro! Espera a gente!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Valeu pela bebida, Blueno!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.32,0:17:29.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What happened to Franky all\Nof a sudden, Kokoro-[/i1]san[/i0]? - OG}O que deu no Franky\Nde repente, dona Kokoro?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.32,0:17:40.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How should I know...\Nhow idiots think? - OG}Sei lá... Não dá pra saber\No que passa na cabeça de idiotas.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I guess things have finally calmed down. - OG}Parece que finalmente se acalmou.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Finalmente se acalmou"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.35,0:17:59.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tinha todos aqueles carpinteiros\Nte perseguindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.52,0:18:02.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's why we ended up\Ngetting dragged into it, too! - OG}Você é que nos arrastou pra isso também!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.23,0:18:05.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que foi inevitável, não disse?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.77,0:18:09.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At any rate, Chopper, I'm surprised\Nyou found out where we were. - OG}Estou surpreso que descobriu\Nonde estávamos, Chopper.{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo seu cheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... É verdade.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.49,0:18:15.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? Come to think of it, where's Sanji? - OG}Verdade! O Sanji não devia estar com vocês?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Robin realmente disse isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.84,0:18:35.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - OG}Aham.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.64,0:18:45.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We all... were prepared for it, right? - OG}Todos nós sabíamos que algo\Nassim poderia acontecer, né?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.86,0:18:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even though it was for a short time, we let Robin, who showed up as an enemy, come on board. - OG}Mesmo sendo por pouco tempo, a Robin\Nera uma inimiga antes de embarcar.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.07,0:18:57.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se ela ficou com medo de repente e fugiu,\Nnão ficaria satisfeito.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.24,0:19:02.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Isn't it about time\Nfor us to settle this matter... - OG}Acho que está na hora de resolver isso...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.66,0:19:07.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{as to whether that woman is... foe or friend? - OG}se aquela mulher é amiga... ou inimiga.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.42,0:19:17.18,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\t(0,2000,0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&)}A situação só vai piorar.\NDepois de hoje, nunca mais vou ver vocês.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.89,0:19:24.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you're sure that Robin said that, Chopper? - OG}Tem certeza que a Robin disse isso, Chopper?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.19,0:19:26.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela disse que não nos veria mais depois de hoje.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.82,0:19:37.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It also sounds like she's declaring that she'll do something that could worsen the situation. - OG}Também parece que ela planeja fazer\Nalgo que pode piorar a situação.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look at how big a fuss the attempted assassination of the mayor caused in this town. - OG}Vejam a confusão que a tentativa de\Nassassinato do prefeito causou.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se é possível piorar a situação...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.92,0:19:52.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,só tem uma coisa que ela pode fazer.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Assassinate the mayor for sure this time. - OG}Assassinar o prefeito de vez dessa vez.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.47,0:20:00.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's natural to think that way. - OG}É a conclusão mais natural.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But we know that she's pinning\Nher crime on us on purpose, - OG}Mas sabemos que ela pretende\Ncolocar a culpa na gente,{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.98,0:20:11.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so it's possible that this could be a trap\Nto lure us out to the scene of the crime. - OG}então é possível que seja uma armadilha\Npra nos atrair pra cena do crime.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Trap... - OG}Uma armadilha?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.86,0:20:16.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we're at the spot\Nof the assassination carried out tonight, - OG}Se estivermos presentes no local\Ne na hora do assassinato,{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the crime will easily be pinned on us. - OG}a culpa vai recair sobre nós.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.99,0:20:23.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! You already sound like\NRobin is really our foe! - OG}Ei! Você faz parecer que a Robin\Nrealmente é nossa inimiga!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm talking about the possibility. - OG}Estou dizendo que é uma possibilidade.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not that I've decided on either. - OG}Ainda não tomei uma decisão.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.79,0:20:33.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I already decide either to believe her or not, - OG}Digamos que eu decida\Nagora de um jeito ou de outro.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{if the truth turns out to be \Nthe opposite of that... - OG}Se a verdade acabar sendo o oposto...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.26,0:20:40.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{it'll slow down my reaction. - OG}atrasaria meu tempo de reação.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If something is to happen,\Nit'll be tonight. Are we going? - OG}Se algo vai acontecer,\Nserá essa noite. Vamos?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.19,0:20:56.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me importo de ir... mas tem um problema.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.23,0:21:00.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Sanji{-kun} viu a Robin andando com alguém, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]said the same thing. - OG}O Iceburg disse a mesma coisa.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.49,0:21:06.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She was with someone with a mask on. - OG}Ela estava com alguém usando máscara.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas não era nenhum de nós.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.21,0:21:13.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele deve ser o motivo\Npelo qual a Robin mudou de repente.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Isn't he making Robin do bad things?! - OG}Então não pode ser que ele esteja\Nobrigando a Robin a fazer coisas ruins?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That would be fortune. - OG}Esse seria o melhor cenário.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.93,0:21:23.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If this guy is Robin's real friend,\Nthen that would be misfortune. - OG}O pior cenário seria se esse cara\Nestivesse agindo junto com a Robin.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.10,0:21:29.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But "someone with a mask on"\Ncan't be a clue. That's the problem. - OG}Mas "alguém usando máscara" não é\Numa boa pista. O mistério está longe de ser resolvido.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é o nosso objetivo?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos capturar a Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.82,0:21:37.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Otherwise, we won't know anything. - OG}Caso contrário, nunca vamos descobrir nada.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Verdade. Ficar pensando é perda de tempo.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But, come to think of it... - OG}Pensando bem...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.16,0:21:48.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o Governo Mundial tenta capturar\Naquela mulher há vinte anos,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and yet, it still hasn't happened. - OG}e, mesmo assim, ela continua solta.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.25,0:21:53.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But if we wanna know the truth,\Nthat's the only way. - OG}Mas se quisermos saber a verdade,\Nessa é a única opção.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, vou dar o meu melhor também!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.38,0:21:59.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, vamos...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:59.88,0:22:02.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{to Galley-La Company! - OG}pra Galley-La Company!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:07.93,0:22:11.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! The night is coming at last. - OG}Droga! Está escurecendo.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.94,0:22:16.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Paulie-san! This is it!\NThe backstreets will become dangerous soon. - OG}{\q2}Paulie! Temos que encerrar a busca!\NAs ruas dos fundos vão ficar perigosas.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, vamos voltar.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:19.69,0:22:20.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna head to the main office. - OG}Vou pro escritório principal.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:22.53,0:22:25.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal! Estamos voltando!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.91,0:22:30.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha! Apareça!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:30.58,0:22:33.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você está se escondendo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:33.67,0:22:37.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha! Aquele maldito...!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:37.46,0:22:40.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achei que o cara tinha pelo menos um pouco de coragem.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:41.72,0:22:44.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas ele nem aparece.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.13,0:22:47.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But Bro, the entire island holds\Na grudge against them right now. - OG}Mas Bro, a ilha inteira\Nestá atrás deles agora.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:48.47,0:22:51.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's right. They must be running from place to place. - OG}Ela tem razão. Aposto que estão\Ncorrendo de um lado pro outro feito ratos.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.89,0:22:56.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By the way, what's the matter?\NWhat're you guys doing? - OG}Mas está tudo bem?\NO que há com vocês dois?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Somos vulneráveis a\Nventos fortes de frente.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.48,0:23:05.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais importante, Bro, seu jeito de\Nesbravejar hoje é diferente do normal.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.57,0:23:09.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Letting stuff build up inside you isn't like you. - OG}Guardar as coisas pra si não combina com você.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.16,0:23:13.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up! I'm like that this week! - OG}Me dá um tempo! Essa semana\Nestou assim mesmo!{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.20,0:23:14.75,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bro!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.50,0:23:14.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.75,0:23:17.71,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bro! Bro!\N– Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:16.21,0:23:17.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São o Zambai e os outros!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.21,0:23:22.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bro! Você bateu naqueles desgraçados?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:22.76,0:23:24.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, ainda não.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.13,0:23:26.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There was some crazy interference. They got away. - OG}Teve uma interferência maluca,\Nentão escaparam.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:26.93,0:23:27.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:27.97,0:23:30.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles escaparam de você\Nmesmo quando estava bravo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.68,0:23:33.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What strong luck they have! - OG}Que filhos da mãe sortudos...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:33.22,0:23:37.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see. Since that weak long-nosed guy\Nwas fixing their ship all by himself, - OG}Entendo. Eu pensei que você\Ntinha batido nos outros{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:37.40,0:23:42.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I just assumed that you beat up the others. - OG}já que aquele narigudo fraco\Nestava consertando o navio deles sozinho.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:42.94,0:23:45.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Vocês encontraram um deles?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, no navio deles.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:51.83,0:23:54.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se vocês encontraram um deles,\Nfica fácil.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can use him to drag them all out! - OG}Podemos usá-lo pra fazer\Ntodos eles aparecerem!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:59.79,0:24:02.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bro is showing his bad guy face. - OG}O Bro tá com a cara de vilão.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:04.46,0:24:08.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well then, you guys! Starting now,\Nmarch throughout the town... - OG}Então, pessoal! Quero que\Nvocês saiam marchando pela cidade...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:09.47,0:24:11.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,gritando: "Capturamos o narigudo!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you don't want him to sink in theat the bottom of the sea, come to the warehouse under the bridge! - OG}Se não querem que ele durma com os peixes,\Nvenham ao armazém debaixo da ponte!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:15.89,0:24:19.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky manda lembranças!"
Dialogue: 5,0:24:21.73,0:24:26.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To make it true,\NI'm gonna go kidnap long-nose. - OG}Vou sequestrar aquele narigudo\Ne tornar isso verdade.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:26.65,0:24:30.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, Bro! Deixa com a gente!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:48.51,0:24:52.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– A Aqua Laguna está vindo!\N– A Aqua Laguna está vindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:52.60,0:24:56.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós somos a Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:56.68,0:24:59.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So what's going on with those culprits? - OG}E aí, e aqueles assassinos?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:59.52,0:25:02.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard that they haven't been caught after all. - OG}Ouvi dizer que ainda não foram capturados.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:02.11,0:25:06.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que perturbador. Aah, que saco...
Dialogue: 5,0:25:06.15,0:25:10.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's said that hey might attack again tonight\Nin the confusion of the storm. - OG}Ouvi dizer que podem atacar de novo\Nessa noite na confusão da tempestade.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:10.53,0:25:13.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Aqua Laguna está aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:13.70,0:25:15.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas vai ser uma loucura essa noite.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:15.83,0:25:20.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard that all the craftsmen\Nwill be guarding the main office. - OG}Ouvi que todos os carpinteiros\Nvão guardar o escritório principal.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:20.04,0:25:22.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Isso é bem sério!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:22.50,0:25:26.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantos são os Piratas do Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:26.50,0:25:31.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Some people said 50. Others said 100. - OG}Alguns dizem cinquenta... outros dizem\Nque é perto de cem.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:31.09,0:25:33.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The captain's got a 100 million\Nbounty on his head, after all. - OG}O capitão tem uma recompensa de 100 milhões, afinal.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:33.80,0:25:38.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguns disseram que 3.000 dos seus homens\Navançariam pelo mar!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:38.14,0:25:40.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso parece totalmente perigoso!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:46.57,0:25:50.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Galley-La Company! Formem uma linha\Ne não deixem nenhuma brecha!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:50.61,0:25:52.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:52.61,0:25:55.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem nem um rato entrar!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:55.24,0:25:57.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:13.43,0:26:15.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venham!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:16.97,0:26:20.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, coo coo! Be quiet, Tilestone! - OG}Cala a boca! Fica quieto, Tilestone!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:22.06,0:26:24.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was told that they weren't on the sea train. - OG}Me disseram que eles não estavam no sea train.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:25.40,0:26:28.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then they're still somewhere\Non this island, huh? - OG}Então ainda estão em algum lugar\Nna ilha, né?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:28.98,0:26:32.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas seriam idiotas se realmente aparecessem\Ncom toda essa segurança.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:33.36,0:26:37.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ouvi que um idiota invadiu aqui\Nno meio do dia hoje.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:38.54,0:26:40.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't think using your common sense. - OG}Senso comum não se aplica a eles.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:41.45,0:26:43.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:43.83,0:26:46.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,eles não precisam ir tão longe.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:46.58,0:26:48.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estão fazendo isso por conta própria.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:49.55,0:26:50.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're treating me like a king. - OG}É como se eu fosse um rei.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:51.38,0:26:55.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A propósito, por que você colocou o cartaz de\Nprocurada da Nico Robin no seu quarto?
Dialogue: 5,0:26:56.80,0:26:57.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you curious? - OG}{Does it bother you? - JT}Curioso?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:00.39,0:27:00.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um pouco.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:05.44,0:27:07.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É melhor que você não saiba.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:10.94,0:27:13.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela é... um demônio.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:40.93,0:27:43.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tons of people are guarding the place. - OG}{Tons of people are guarding the entrance. - JT}Tem muitos guardas no local...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:43.47,0:27:45.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É meio longe.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:45.35,0:27:49.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can just stretch your arm and go flying there, right? But after the commotion starts, okay? - OG}{Can't you just stretch your arm and fly in? After the commotion starts, got it? - JT}Você estica o braço e voa até lá,\Nmas só depois da confusão começar, tá?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:49.36,0:27:55.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. If we cause a commotion before they do,\Nthey'll just take advantage of it. - OG}{\q2}É. Se a gente causar a confusão antes deles,\Neles é que terão a vantagem.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:55.07,0:27:56.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escutem!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:56.95,0:27:59.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não percam nem o menor movimento!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:59.66,0:28:04.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=15}===============================DIALOGUE============================
